      "text": "You're driving so fast.",
      "zh": "你開車太快了。",
      "ja": "運転が速すぎます。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "zh": "喔不。",
      "ja": "ああ、いやだ。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We're late.",
