      "ja": "遅れています。",
      "time": "00:01:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I should have checked the time.",
      "zh": "我應該要看時間的。",
      "ja": "時間を確認すべきでした。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is everything all right?",
      "zh": "一切都好嗎？",
      "ja": "大丈夫ですか？",
