    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Step down carefully now.",
      "zh": "現在小心地下車。",
      "ja": "今、気をつけて降りてください。",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look at all the boats.",
      "zh": "看看所有的船。",
      "ja": "すべての船を見てください。",
      "time": "00:01:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's a perfect day for sailing.",
      "zh": "今天是航海的完美天氣。",
      "ja": "航海にぴったりの日です。",
