      "ja": "一緒にいてください。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Keep going.",
      "zh": "繼續前進。",
      "ja": "進み続けて。",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Don't stop.",
      "zh": "不要停。",
      "ja": "止まらないで。",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hurry.",
      "zh": "快點。",
      "ja": "急いで。",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We're late.",
      "zh": "我們遲到了。",
      "ja": "遅れています。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah!",
