      "ja": "心の準備は重傷を防ぐのに役立ちます。",
      "time": "00:05:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It helps the body adapt to water pressure and improve swimming performance.",
      "zh": "它幫助身體適應水壓並提升游泳表現。",
      "ja": "体が水圧に適応し、泳ぎのパフォーマンスを向上させます。",
      "time": "00:05:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The water is cool.",
      "zh": "水很涼。",
      "ja": "水が冷たい。",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am here.",
      "zh": "我來了。",
      "ja": "ここにいます。",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "zh": "別擔心。",
      "ja": "心配しないで。",
      "time": "00:05:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you Mom.",
      "zh": "謝謝媽媽。",
      "ja": "ありがとうママ。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You did it.",
      "zh": "你做到了。",
      "ja": "できたね。",
      "time": "00:05:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good job.",
      "zh": "幹得好。",
      "ja": "よくやった。",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look out.",
      "zh": "小心。",
      "ja": "気をつけて。",
      "time": "00:05:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here comes a big one.",
      "zh": "大浪來了。",
      "ja": "大きいのが来るよ。",
      "time": "00:05:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The splice of death.",
      "zh": "死亡浪。",
      "ja": "死の波。",
      "time": "00:06:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah we got you.",
      "zh": "是的，我們抓到了你。",
      "ja": "そう、捕まえたよ。",
      "time": "00:06:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right big smiles everyone.",
      "zh": "好，大家笑一個。",
      "ja": "さあ、みんな笑って。",
      "time": "00:06:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Say cheese.",
      "zh": "說茄子。",
      "ja": "チーズと言って。",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Cheese.",
      "zh": "茄子。",
      "ja": "チーズ。",
      "time": "00:06:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Careful sweetie you're getting us all wet.",
      "zh": "小心親愛的，你弄濕我們了。",
      "ja": "気をつけて、かわい子ちゃん、みんな濡れちゃうよ。",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey splashy fun.",
      "zh": "嘿，潑水樂趣。",
      "ja": "ねえ、水しぶき楽しいね。",
      "time": "00:06:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Perfect.",
      "zh": "完美。",
      "ja": "完璧。",
      "time": "00:06:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One more for the album.",
      "zh": "再拍一張留念。",
      "ja": "アルバム用にもう一枚。",
      "time": "00:06:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Looking into the camera we will take a commemorative photo.",
      "zh": "看著鏡頭，我們要拍紀念照。",
      "ja": "カメラを見て記念写真を撮ります。",
      "time": "00:06:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One, two, three, smile.",
      "zh": "一、二、三，笑一個。",
      "ja": "いち、に、さん、はいチーズ。",
      "time": "00:06:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dry yourself off to avoid catching a cold.",
      "zh": "擦乾身體以免感冒。",
      "ja": "風邪をひかないように体を乾かして。",
      "time": "00:06:26"
