      "ja": "船に乗ってお土産を買いに行きます。",
      "time": "00:06:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We will buy gifts for our grandparents.",
      "zh": "我們會買禮物給祖父母。",
      "ja": "祖父母への贈り物を買います。",
      "time": "00:06:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's right.",
      "zh": "沒錯。",
      "ja": "そうです。",
      "time": "00:06:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you guys ready?",
      "zh": "你們準備好了嗎？",
      "ja": "みんな準備できた？",
      "time": "00:06:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What shirt should I wear?",
      "zh": "我該穿什麼襯衫？",
      "ja": "どのシャツを着ようかな？",
      "time": "00:06:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We will wear similar clothes.",
      "zh": "我們會穿相似的衣服。",
      "ja": "似た服を着ます。",
      "time": "00:06:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:06:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:07:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you know that it's a...",
      "zh": "你知道那是...",
      "ja": "それが何か知ってる？",
      "time": "00:07:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow this stock is so long.",
      "zh": "哇，這排隊好長。",
      "ja": "わあ、この列はとても長い。",
      "time": "00:07:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It sure is.",
      "zh": "真的很長。",
      "ja": "本当にそうだね。",
      "time": "00:07:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We're almost at the end.",
      "zh": "我們快到尾端了。",
      "ja": "もうすぐ終わりです。",
      "time": "00:07:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look at all the boats in the harbor.",
      "zh": "看看港口裡的船。",
      "ja": "港のすべての船を見て。",
      "time": "00:07:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can we go on the big one?",
      "zh": "我們可以去那艘大船嗎？",
      "ja": "あの大きいのに乗れる？",
      "time": "00:07:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe tomorrow.",
      "zh": "也許明天。",
      "ja": "多分明日ね。",
      "time": "00:07:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today we're exploring the harbor.",
      "zh": "今天我們在探索港口。",
      "ja": "今日は港を探検します。",
      "time": "00:07:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow look at the corn.",
