      "ja": "わあ、トウモロコシを見て。",
      "time": "00:07:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can we get some?",
      "zh": "我們可以買一些嗎？",
      "ja": "いくつか買ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:07:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "可以。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:07:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's get a couple for a snack.",
      "zh": "我們買幾根當點心。",
      "ja": "おやつにいくつか買いましょう。",
      "time": "00:07:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can we buy potatoes as a gift for our grandparents?",
