      "ja": "祖父母への贈り物にジャガイモを買ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:07:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Potatoes will spoil and become unhealthy.",
      "zh": "馬鈴薯會壞掉變得不健康。",
      "ja": "ジャガイモは腐って健康に良くなくなります。",
      "time": "00:07:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dad, can I buy a ball as a gift for grandpa?",
      "zh": "爸爸，我可以買球當禮物給爺爺嗎？",
      "ja": "パパ、祖父への贈り物にボールを買ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:07:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He was too old to play football.",
      "zh": "他太老了不能踢足球。",
      "ja": "彼は年を取りすぎてサッカーができません。",
      "time": "00:07:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What should we buy?",
      "zh": "我們該買什麼？",
      "ja": "何を買うべき？",
      "time": "00:07:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm, good question.",
      "zh": "嗯，好問題。",
      "ja": "うーん、いい質問だね。",
      "time": "00:07:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What about a basket?",
      "zh": "買個籃子怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "バスケットはどう？",
      "time": "00:07:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Or maybe some pottery?",
      "zh": "或者一些陶器？",
      "ja": "それとも陶器？",
      "time": "00:08:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They like handmade things.",
      "zh": "他們喜歡手工藝品。",
      "ja": "彼らは手作りのものが好きです。",
      "time": "00:08:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's a great idea.",
      "zh": "那是個好主意。",
      "ja": "それはいいアイデアだ。",
      "time": "00:08:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's keep looking.",
      "zh": "我們繼續找。",
      "ja": "探し続けましょう。",
      "time": "00:08:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:08:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My grandfather really likes drinking tea.",
      "zh": "我爺爺很喜歡喝茶。",
      "ja": "私の祖父はお茶を飲むのが大好きです。",
      "time": "00:08:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A great idea.",
      "zh": "好主意。",
      "ja": "いいアイデアです。",
      "time": "00:08:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We'll buy a bracelet as a gift for grandma.",
      "zh": "我們會買手鐲當禮物給奶奶。",
      "ja": "祖母への贈り物にブレスレットを買います。",
      "time": "00:08:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow it's beautiful.",
      "zh": "哇，好漂亮。",
      "ja": "わあ、美しい。",
      "time": "00:08:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's a lovely choice.",
      "zh": "這是個可愛的選擇。",
      "ja": "素敵な選択です。",
      "time": "00:08:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That will be $20.",
      "zh": "這是20美元。",
      "ja": "20ドルになります。",
      "time": "00:08:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here you are.",
      "zh": "給你。",
      "ja": "どうぞ。",
      "time": "00:08:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:08:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Enjoy.",
      "zh": "請享用。",
      "ja": "お楽しみください。",
      "time": "00:08:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Grandma will love it.",
      "zh": "奶奶會喜歡的。",
      "ja": "祖母は喜ぶでしょう。",
      "time": "00:08:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Isn't that just a perfect view kids?",
      "zh": "這不是完美的景色嗎，孩子們？",
      "ja": "これは完璧な景色だね、みんな？",
      "time": "00:08:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:08:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look how big this ship is.",
      "zh": "看看這艘船有多大。",
      "ja": "この船がどれほど大きいか見て。",
      "time": "00:08:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't wait to see you inside.",
      "zh": "我迫不及待想帶你們進去看。",
      "ja": "中を見るのが待ちきれません。",
      "time": "00:08:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:08:40"
    }
  ]
}